verses.verse: To the chief <S%H5329>Musician,<s%> <S%H516>Al-taschith,<s%> A <S%H4210>Psalm<s%> or <S%H7892>Song<s%> of <S%H623>Asaph.<s%> Unto thee, O <S%H430>God,<s%> do we give <S%H3034>thanks,<s%> unto thee do we give <S%H3034>thanks:<s%> for that thy <S%H8034>name<s%> is <S%H7138>near<s%> thy wondrous <S%H6381>works<s%> <S%H5608>declare.<s%>
The <S%H776>earth<s%> and <S%H3605>all<s%> the <S%H3427>inhabitants<s%> thereof are <S%H4127>dissolved:<s%> <S%H595>I<s%> bear <S%H8505>up<s%> the <S%H5982>pillars<s%> of it. <S%H5542>Selah.<s%>
I <S%H559>said<s%> unto the <S%H1984>fools,<s%> Deal not <S%H408>foolishly:<s%> <S%H1984><s%> and to the <S%H7563>wicked,<s%> Lift not <S%H7311>up<s%> <S%H408><s%> the horn: <S%H7161><s%>
Lift not <S%H7311>up<s%> <S%H408><s%> your <S%H7161>horn<s%> on <S%H4791>high:<s%> <S%H1696>speak<s%> not with a <S%H6277>stiff<s%> <S%H6677>neck.<s%>

For <S%H3588><s%> <S%H7311>promotion<s%> cometh <S%H3808>neither<s%> from the <S%H4480>east,<s%> <S%H4161><s%> nor from the <S%H4480>west,<s%> <S%H4628><s%> <S%H3808>nor<s%> from the <S%H4480>south.<s%> <S%H4057><s%>
But <S%H3588><s%> <S%H430>God<s%> is the <S%H8199>judge:<s%> he putteth <S%H8213>down<s%> <S%H2088>one,<s%> and <S%H7311>setteth<s%> up <S%H2088>another.<s%>

For <S%H3588><s%> in the <S%H3027>hand<s%> of the <S%H3068>LORD<s%> there is a <S%H3563>cup,<s%> and the <S%H3196>wine<s%> is <S%H2560>red;<s%> it is <S%H4392>full<s%> of <S%H4538>mixture;<s%> and he poureth <S%H5064>out<s%> of the <S%H4480>same:<s%> <S%H2088><s%> <S%H389>but<s%> the <S%H8105>dregs<s%> thereof, <S%H3605>all<s%> the <S%H7563>wicked<s%> of the <S%H776>earth<s%> shall wring them <S%H4680>out,<s%> and <S%H8354>drink<s%> them.
But <S%H589>I<s%> will <S%H5046>declare<s%> <S%H5769>forever;<s%> I will sing <S%H2167>praises<s%> to the <S%H430>God<s%> of <S%H3290>Jacob.<s%>
All <S%H3605><s%> the <S%H7161>horns<s%> of the <S%H7563>wicked<s%> also will I cut <S%H1438>off;<s%> but the <S%H7161>horns<s%> of the <S%H6662>righteous<s%> shall be <S%H7311>exalted.<s%>
